title: Lick Library - How To Play Fast Vol. 1&2 - DVDRip
description:
Learn some serious shredding technique with Dave Kilminster.

This DVD will help you get your shredding up to warp factor! Learn some astounding fretburning techniques including fast legato, arpeggios, speed picking, string skipping.

The second volume of this series will teach you even more astounding fretburning techniques including chromatic runs, sweep picking, open string phrases, sliding techniques, tapping, and an arsenal of speed building licks!
